text: Ebe W. Tunnell was an American Democratic Party politician who served as governor of Delaware from 1897 to 1901. During his tenure various measures were introducedAt a General Assembly begun at dover, in the Delaware State, ... the following Acts were passed 1895-1897 such as a number of labor laws.Title: January 1900 : Bulletin of the United States Bureau of Labor, No. 26, Volume V, P.235 ==References== Category:Governors of Delaware Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
